00:05:07.800 --> 00:05:10.550
global exchange rates
and stock information?

00:05:10.730 --> 00:05:12.790
The bank has been doing
an asset inventory recently,

00:05:12.790 --> 00:05:14.700
and we discovered
a spare telegraph machine

00:05:14.700 --> 00:05:16.310
listed in storage.

00:05:16.440 --> 00:05:18.120
