00:05:33.480 --> 00:05:34.270
Xian.

00:05:36.400 --> 00:05:37.340
Thank you.

00:05:39.180 --> 00:05:39.740
Alright.

00:05:40.909 --> 00:05:41.430
I'm off.

00:05:41.670 --> 00:05:42.470
Thanks, Xian!

