00:09:43.550 --> 00:09:45.350
Your Excellency the Commander,

00:09:45.430 --> 00:09:49.820
I have repeatedly reported to
the Expeditionary Army Command

00:09:50.320 --> 00:09:53.300
that the current
anti-Japanese forces here,

00:09:53.700 --> 00:09:55.360
local Portuguese merchants,

00:09:55.560 --> 00:09:56.700
pirates from the Lingding Channel,

00:09:56.700 --> 00:09:57.390
and

00:09:58.080 --> 00:09:59.930
Communist guerrillas in Zhongshan

00:09:59.930 --> 00:10:01.250
have all colluded.

00:10:01.800 --> 00:10:03.080
The Portuguese Macau government

00:10:03.080 --> 00:10:05.560
has tolerated their existence.

00:10:05.560 --> 00:10:07.480
To reverse this situation,

00:10:08.010 --> 00:10:10.610
our only option is
to occupy Macau militarily.

00:10:11.900 --> 00:10:14.170
If we occupy Macau,

00:10:14.910 --> 00:10:15.840
we will be able to

00:10:16.060 --> 00:10:17.300
obtain the supplies?

00:10:17.990 --> 00:10:18.050
[The Japanese 23rd Army]

00:10:18.050 --> 00:10:18.980
On the contrary,

00:10:19.120 --> 00:10:19.290
[Matsui Shinji, Commander of
the Independent Infantry 8th Brigade]

00:10:19.290 --> 00:10:21.550
it will only lead to a complete shutdown,

00:10:21.750 --> 00:10:25.350
leaving our Imperial Army
with even fewer supplies than before.

00:10:26.170 --> 00:10:28.170
Furthermore,

00:10:28.300 --> 00:10:29.650
countries like Portugal

00:10:29.650 --> 00:10:33.110
that still maintain trade relations
with our Empire of Japan—

00:10:33.220 --> 00:10:35.770
how many remain worldwide?

00:10:36.340 --> 00:10:37.600
Surely, you wouldn't want to

00:10:37.600 --> 00:10:39.530
sacrifice

00:10:39.910 --> 00:10:42.180
our last remaining supply line from Europe

00:10:42.180 --> 00:10:44.310
for the sake of Macau alone, would you?

00:10:47.870 --> 00:10:48.930
Mr. Yazaki,

00:10:49.550 --> 00:10:52.750
you're not entertaining
such a wild idea as well, are you?

00:10:56.700 --> 00:10:58.570
If the Command cannot accept

00:10:58.800 --> 00:11:02.130
the idea of occupying Macau,

00:11:03.220 --> 00:11:05.060
there is only one way left

00:11:05.530 --> 00:11:06.510
to turn

00:11:07.350 --> 00:11:08.820
the situation around.

00:11:09.510 --> 00:11:10.680
What way?

00:11:15.010 --> 00:11:19.550
This is a new countermeasure plan
I've drawn up.

00:11:20.580 --> 00:11:22.580
Please review it, Your Excellency.

00:11:30.290 --> 00:11:32.060
Encircle Black Hill?

00:11:33.530 --> 00:11:34.050
Yes.

00:11:35.230 --> 00:11:37.590
The Black Hill Guerrilla Unit

00:11:38.200 --> 00:11:40.370
is a crucial link

00:11:40.400 --> 00:11:44.040
in the underground supply route
from Zhongshan to Macau.

00:11:44.560 --> 00:11:47.820
If we can eliminate this guerrilla unit
in a single strike,

00:11:48.130 --> 00:11:49.080
we will sever

00:11:49.080 --> 00:11:51.140
the entire underground supply line.

00:11:59.270 --> 00:12:00.980
Your Excellency the Commander,

00:12:00.980 --> 00:12:03.460
I am personally willing to take

00:12:03.460 --> 00:12:06.260
full responsibility
for any failure of this plan.

00:12:06.980 --> 00:12:09.030
Please approve it.

00:12:15.950 --> 00:12:17.950
What are your opinions, gentlemen?

00:12:20.340 --> 00:12:21.390
I agree.

00:12:27.370 --> 00:12:28.370
Your Excellency.

00:12:29.910 --> 00:12:30.970
Please approve it.

