Take all important supplies!

00:13:15.600 --> 00:13:15.940
Go!

00:13:15.940 --> 00:13:17.000
Retreat! Let's go!

00:13:18.340 --> 00:13:19.340
Take everything!

00:14:02.430 --> 00:14:04.560
All transport operations suspended?

00:14:04.840 --> 00:14:06.270
We have no choice.

00:14:06.930 --> 00:14:07.730
Master Sanhe,

00:14:08.010 --> 00:14:08.810
I understand.

00:14:08.930 --> 00:14:10.130
For the past two years, your men
have been mostly transporting

00:14:10.130 --> 00:14:11.340
supplies for the Resistance,

00:14:11.340 --> 00:14:12.370
earning just a little hard-earned money

00:14:12.370 --> 00:14:13.440
to barely get by.

00:14:13.440 --> 00:14:15.010
Once transport operations stop,

00:14:15.010 --> 00:14:17.540
your men will have a hard time
making a living.

00:14:17.890 --> 00:14:19.550
If there are difficulties...

00:14:19.800 --> 00:14:21.630
Money isn't what I'm concerned about.

00:14:21.630 --> 00:14:23.840
No matter how tough
things get for our men,

00:14:23.840 --> 00:14:25.370
they won't starve to death.

00:14:25.600 --> 00:14:26.920
What I'm worried about is

00:14:26.920 --> 00:14:29.290
this large shipment of tungsten ore
that just arrived.

00:14:29.290 --> 00:14:30.600
We had agreed

00:14:30.600 --> 00:14:31.770
to exchange it

00:14:31.930 --> 00:14:32.860
for the shipment

00:14:32.960 --> 00:14:34.390
of diesel fuel
that Rodrigues brought into

00:14:34.390 --> 00:14:34.980
Macau.

00:14:36.010 --> 00:14:37.870
Once transport operations stop,

00:14:37.980 --> 00:14:40.180
with such important cargo stuck in hand

00:14:40.580 --> 00:14:42.300
and the Japanese inspecting so strictly,

00:14:42.300 --> 00:14:43.670
if time drags on,

00:14:43.940 --> 00:14:45.200
I'm afraid information might leak

00:14:45.200 --> 00:14:46.340
and cause trouble.

00:14:47.440 --> 00:14:49.980
It's precisely because this cargo is
so important

00:14:49.980 --> 00:14:51.680
that without the Guerrilla Unit's escort,

00:14:51.680 --> 00:14:53.210
the risk is simply too high.

00:14:53.670 --> 00:14:54.370
That's right.

00:14:54.370 --> 00:14:55.170
Master Sanhe,

00:14:55.320 --> 00:14:56.960
we'll have to ask you

00:14:56.960 --> 00:14:58.530
to find a way to hide
this batch of goods for now.

00:14:58.530 --> 00:14:59.180
Alright.

00:14:59.510 --> 00:15:01.290
I'll return to Zhongshan overnight

00:15:01.290 --> 00:15:03.580
and hide the tungsten ore
in the Xi River first,

00:15:03.580 --> 00:15:05.180
so the Japanese won't find it.

00:15:05.180 --> 00:15:06.840
The most important thing right now

00:15:06.840 --> 00:15:07.770
isn't the cargo,

00:15:08.150 --> 00:15:08.880
but...

00:15:09.050 --> 00:15:10.430
how to help Captain Ou and his men

00:15:10.430 --> 00:15:11.830
get through this crisis.

00:15:12.270 --> 00:15:12.940
Indeed.

00:15:13.150 --> 00:15:14.510
The encrypted telegram
from the Guerrilla Unit says

00:15:14.510 --> 00:15:16.770
that dozens of wounded guerrillas
can't move with the team,

00:15:16.770 --> 00:15:18.340
especially the critically injured.

00:15:18.340 --> 00:15:19.980
They urgently need surgery now,

00:15:19.980 --> 00:15:22.510
but Zhongshan doesn't have
the necessary conditions.

00:15:22.510 --> 00:15:23.840
They are asking if we in Macau

00:15:23.840 --> 00:15:25.170
can think of a solution.

00:15:26.150 --> 00:15:26.870
Dr. Ke,

00:15:27.440 --> 00:15:28.750
aren't the operating rooms
at Kiang Wu Hospital

00:15:28.750 --> 00:15:30.060
ready for use?

00:15:30.510 --> 00:15:32.180
The surgical equipment is all in place,

00:15:32.180 --> 00:15:34.460
but the application to open
the operating rooms

00:15:34.460 --> 00:15:36.860
is still being held up
by the Health Bureau.

00:15:37.190 --> 00:15:39.590
Why is it being held up
by the Health Bureau?

00:15:39.650 --> 00:15:42.960
The Portuguese Macau government has long
discriminated against Chinese doctors.

00:15:42.960 --> 00:15:43.820
The Health Bureau has regulations

00:15:43.820 --> 00:15:44.530
that in Macau,

00:15:44.530 --> 00:15:45.870
only certified

00:15:45.870 --> 00:15:47.060
Portuguese surgeons

00:15:47.060 --> 00:15:48.870
are qualified to perform surgeries.

00:15:48.870 --> 00:15:50.820
Chinese doctors can't perform surgeries
without authorization.

00:15:50.820 --> 00:15:52.480
We need approval from the Health Bureau,

00:15:52.480 --> 00:15:53.840
which then reports to
the Executive Council.

00:15:53.840 --> 00:15:54.930
In short, there are piles of procedures,

00:15:54.930 --> 00:15:56.930
and approval won't come for months.

00:15:56.940 --> 00:15:58.270
Those damn foreigners.

00:15:58.750 --> 00:16:00.350
The situation is urgent now.

00:16:00.580 --> 00:16:01.940
We don't have time to wait for them

00:16:01.940 --> 00:16:03.740
to go through their procedures.

00:16:03.790 --> 00:16:04.840
I'll go back immediately and mobilize

00:16:04.840 --> 00:16:06.510
all medical staff

00:16:07.930 --> 00:16:09.220
to jointly petition the Governor

00:16:09.220 --> 00:16:13.300
for urgent special authorization to allow
Kiang Wu Hospital to perform surgery.

00:16:13.300 --> 00:16:15.170
Once the surgical authorization is
approved,

00:16:15.170 --> 00:16:16.250
Master Sanhe, I hope you

00:16:16.250 --> 00:16:18.780
can transport the wounded
to Macau promptly.

00:16:18.980 --> 00:16:20.060
You can count on me.

